casebody.data:
Luis Miguel Fontal VASQUEZ and Jose Manuel Otero, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Aliec Lazo MARTINEZ, etc., et al., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-1628 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. NOVEMBER 03, 2017 ROTHENBERG, C.J., and FERNANDEZ and LUCK, JJ., concur.

Upon the Court's own motion, it is ordered that this appeal from the Circuit Court for Miami-Dade County, Florida is dismissed for failure to comply with this Court's order dated September 18, 2017, and with the Florida Rules of Appellate Procedure.
